<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186803>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Dorsal view of anterior end of Pyrgopolon ctenactis (Mørch, 1863) from Station 212, Santa Barbara, Bonaire, collected, determined and presented by ten Hove, BM (NH) 1971: 230. Note operculum inserted independently of branchial radioles of both sides, i. e., from the middle of the anterior end of the thorax." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/186803/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

